Interface Provider<T>

Type Parameters:
T - 
public interface Provider<T>

Provides given object when get() is called, then release it when release() is. Notice implementors are free to allow (or not) multiple calls to get to provide the same instance, while implementors should guarantee that same number of release() than the number of get() will release the object provided by this Provider.
